### the Author
My name is Al-Ahmadgaid B. Asaad, a statistician, programmer and [blogger](http://alstatr.blogspot.com/). I have a degree on Bachelor of Science in Statistics from Iligan Institute of Technology of the Mindanao State University. Currently, I hold three positions: 
 1. Consultant
 2. Researcher 
 3. Statistician

I am  accept consultation on R programming language for Masteral Theses and PhD Dissertation.
